   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2274, recto: (1) A half-tremis has come (2) to me from you, (3) Victor (son of) Samuel, (4) for your poll tax in (5) the demosion of the eleventh indiction, total one-sixth solidus.  (6) Epiph 18, indiction 11.  Stephen signs.  (7) Papnoute signs.  (8) Dioskoros signs.  (10) Aristophanes (11) wrote.</ab>
